you could help the rest of your life?

27
00:01:34,046 --> 00:01:36,693
You can't trick those souls
into staying here.

28
00:01:36,696 --> 00:01:40,780
I will release
all your precious souls.

29
00:01:40,817 --> 00:01:44,550
