32
00:01:56,006 --> 00:01:58,142
I was supposed
to be on that plane, Melinda,

33
00:01:58,148 --> 00:02:00,140
I can't believe Andrea
it's dead.

34
00:02:00,648 --> 00:02:01,941
How'd it happen?

35
00:02:01,947 --> 00:02:05,720
She was driving
to your apartment in the city.

36
00:02:06,498 --> 00:02:08,911
She tried so hard
to reach you.

37
00:02:09,408 --> 00:02:12,501
