path of the plane.

38
00:02:12,505 --> 00:02:15,973
- Do you think she suffered?
- No.

39
00:02:19,306 --> 00:02:21,561
No, I don't think so.

40
00:02:21,718 --> 00:02:23,911
This can't be happening!

41
00:02:27,778 --> 00:02:30,831
