- I've been looking for you, where are you?

44
00:03:01,305 --> 00:03:03,412
At the store.
I'm so scared!

45
00:03:03,416 --> 00:03:06,341
- Well, can you get to my house?
- I don't know!

46
00:03:06,348 --> 00:03:10,811
Ok. I'll come to you.
I have really good news.

47
00:03:10,835 --> 00:03:12,910
Hello?!

48
00:03:12,915 --> 00:03:14,882
How is she calling you?

49
00:03:15,038 --> 00:03:18,500
