54
00:03:50,868 --> 00:03:53,772
Andrea, I've been
so worried about you!

55
00:03:53,778 --> 00:03:57,371
- Tell me everything's gonna be ok.
- I think maybe it is.

56
00:03:57,376 --> 00:03:59,931
You may not really be dead.

57
00:04:00,085 --> 00:04:02,082
- What?
