127
00:09:07,166 --> 00:09:09,612
- We're gonna be ok.
- Thank you.

128
00:09:10,466 --> 00:09:12,470
Well, there you have it
from a local merchant.

129
00:09:12,476 --> 00:09:16,382
This town is grieving, but determined
