130
00:09:27,986 --> 00:09:31,081
Andrea?...
Are you here?

131
00:09:33,955 --> 00:09:36,712
I just want
to talk to you, please.

132
00:09:36,716 --> 00:09:39,342
I know that you're scared.

133
00:10:34,268 --> 00:10:37,471
- Where's andrea?
- I'll be glad to take a message.

134
00:10:37,476 --> 00:10:41,252
- What are you doing to her?
