135
00:10:41,257 --> 00:10:44,333
- She's doing it all to herself.
- Who are you?

136
00:10:44,338 --> 00:10:47,341
I was alive once.
Just like you.

137
00:10:47,346 --> 00:10:51,380
- ...I had names, I had lis.
- Romano... Is that your name?

138
00:10:51,385 --> 00:10:53,561
- I'm just a humble teacher.
- Teacher?

139
00:10:53,565 --> 00:10:56,152
Trying to spread the word.

140
00:10:56,156 --> 00:10:59,643
- Much like yourself.
- What are you doing here? What do you want?

141
00:10:59,648 --> 00:11:01,932
- I have what I want.
- No. No, you don'T.

142
00:11:01,938 --> 00:11:06,311
Andrea will not go with you. I
