- Will you buy me food?
- Yes.

184
00:14:24,148 --> 00:14:26,752
- Follow me.
- Great!

185
00:14:27,276 --> 00:14:29,430
I don't teach
the supernatural.

186
00:14:29,435 --> 00:14:32,913
I teach society's need to believe
in the supernatural,

187
00:14:32,915 --> 00:14:35,842
